### 1.3 Fix: Timeout in `enroll.py`

```python
# Vorher (hängt für immer):
while f.readImage() == False:
    pass

# Nachher:
def wait_for_finger(sensor, timeout=30):
    start = time.time()
    while not sensor.readImage():
        if time.time() - start > timeout:
            raise TimeoutError("Kein Finger nach 30s")
        time.sleep(0.1)
```

