## Phase 4 — Autostart & Integration

### 4.1 systemd Service (Pi)

```ini
# /etc/systemd/system/retroconsole-login.service
[Unit]
Description=RetroConsole Login UI
After=graphical.target

[Service]
User=pi
Environment=DISPLAY=:0
ExecStart=/usr/bin/python3 /home/pi/RetroConsole_OS/start.py
Restart=always
RestartSec=3

[Install]
WantedBy=graphical.target
```

```bash
sudo systemctl enable retroconsole-login.service
sudo systemctl start retroconsole-login.service
```

### 4.2 `settings.json` (neue Config-Datei)

```json
{
  "hardware": {
    "fingerprint_port": "/dev/ttyAMA0",
    "fingerprint_baud": 57600,
    "ws2812b_pin": 10,
    "ws2812b_count": 16
  },
  "ui": {
    "fullscreen": true,
    "resolution": [1920, 1080],
    "scan_timeout_sec": 5,
    "enroll_timeout_sec": 30,
    "theme": "cyber_retro"
  },
  "emulationstation": {
    "binary": "emulationstation",
    "users_base_dir": "/home/pi/users"
  }
}
```

